@startuml
title Campaign State Transition Diagram

initial state : Start
    :Start --> Assigned : Manager and Staff are assigned
    :Assigned --> Approved : Everything approved, contract signed
    :Approved --> AdvertsPrepared : Adverts prepared during campaign
    :AdvertsPrepared --> AdvertsScheduled : Approve and schedule adverts
    :AdvertsScheduled --> AdvertsRunning : Run the adverts
    :AdvertsRunning --> ExtendOrAdjust : Extension or adjustment of the campaign
    :ExtendOrAdjust --> AdvertsRunning : Continue running after extension/adjustment
    :AdvertsRunning --> CampaignCompleted : All adverts have finished
    :CampaignCompleted --> FinalStatementPrepared : Prepare final statement
    :FinalStatementPrepared --> PaymentHandling : Handle payment
    :PaymentHandling --> Paid : Full amount paid, mark as paid
    :Paid --> Archived : Archive campaign and release staff

@enduml
